AVR HW configuration
====================

Attached HW
===========
1) RTC PCB:
- AT24C32: EEPROM (4094x8);
- DS3231: RTC;

Cristal
=======
Frequency: 7.3728MHz

Flashing target
===============
sudo avarice --erase --program --file console-test --part atmega32 --jtag /dev/ttyUSB1 --verify --reset-srst

